cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with the application of deep convolutional neural networks for the classification of lung tissue patterns in medical images. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of transfer learning from general texture classification also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The paper also involves the analysis of medical images, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
